{"tid":2157644,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴選好味雪條","createTime":"2020-08-15T07:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T14:44:50.000Z","uid":207900,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a706a565574692d0fdf4a329e5bab125c7f250d1","tid":2157644,"uid":207900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/4fNJhAw8JTZsaBC99\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2F4fNJhAw8JTZsaBC99&h=2c9d5d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/yhzJjMnGnsnbEA298\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2FyhzJjMnGnsnbEA298&h=8e14f9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定係鳳仙雪條，沒有之一<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a255751b8658ac4a4cb7a6ddd9407fa92c15d14e","tid":2157644,"uid":207900,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ycs4T3K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcs4T3K.jpg&h=77095991&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQM9kJK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQM9kJK.jpg&h=d581a011&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"699549abd43a01045b4cfbb4983eb6d10cdb47ab","tid":2157644,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:23:39.000Z","msg":"黑牛"},{"pid":"b6cf1993b34d1c38225be744480f0e416919e521","tid":2157644,"uid":227275,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"依隻同埋檸檬冰 橙冰都唔見晒 屌"},{"pid":"e7d20ce86e17e6517a95d4efc54c16ea151c5666","tid":2157644,"uid":207900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6cf1993b34d1c38225be744480f0e416919e521","tid":2157644,"uid":227275,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"依隻同埋檸檬冰 橙冰都唔見晒 屌"},"citedB